        "Description": "Good evening, agent!\r\rYour targets are Valentine Wilton who secretly works as a thief and his goal is to steal the race winner&apos;s cup, Ted Montgomery who creates and finds different ways to steal the cup, Kent Wakefield who is Ted&apos;s worker and finally Jimeno Vasquez who does all the dirty work. Be careful agent, those men are not afraid to cause collateral damage.\r\rGood luck!",
